title: Congressman Roger Marshall’s Son Won’t Stop Dabbing During Swearing In Ceremony With Paul Ryan
text:
Congressman Roger Marshall’s Son Won’t Stop Dabbing During Swearing In Ceremony With Paul Ryan Riggs | 
— Jeremy Art (@cspanJeremy) January 3, 2017 
Be more of a dork Paul Ryan. Be more out of touch. 
“Can you put your hand down?” 
“Are you gonna sneeze is that it?” 
Come on dude. Dabbing. It’s fucking 2017. Dabbing’s literally been in, gone out, come back in HOT, and now is so through the ringer that it’s a hilarious mockery of itself. It’s reached the rarest level of trends. It’s like a 5-star trend or a trend medal of honor (shoutout ZBT). We got funny fat kids and Chaps slide-dabbing for fucks sake. Best dab in NHL history? Many people are saying it. pic.twitter.com/BANn6r7ulD
